title: 3bed/2ba Hopkins - AUG 1st Love DOGS!
posting_body: ['TEXT', 'show contact info', 'FOR SHOWINGS', '$1855 | 3 Bedroom | 2 Bath | 1300 sq ft. | Basement w/ 2nd Bath- 3rd bed | Dishwasher | Storage | Washer/Dryer |', 'Check out this UPDATED duplex located in the heart of Hopkins, MN and walking distance to the great shops and restaurants of downtown Hopkins.', 'This side by side duplex has all the amenities of a 3 bed 2 bath single family home.', 'Sitting on a double lot there is plenty of yard space for your dog, children and outdoor fun...', 'In addition, the unit has a large living space in the basement.', 'Cozy, spacious and ready for you to call it home!', 'Renter is responsible for all utilities.', 'Please TEXT', 'show contact info', 'for SHOWING information.', 'Property is not Sec 8 approved', 'Income Requirement: 3x Rent', '*TEXT', 'show contact info', 'for Questions*', 'A little about the owners...', 'We love people, community and sharing great spaces with our renters.', 'We do live in the unit next door, but believe your home is your home', 'and we are just stewards of the property.', 'Good luck with your search and if the stars align we look forward to being your new neighbors!']
